Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.70,0:01:39.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要哦  不要不要
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.87,0:01:43.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子要跟在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.61,0:01:47.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,库库  库库  库库
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.24,0:01:48.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这仆从  快点放手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.62,0:01:50.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.65,0:01:51.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要闹了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.19,0:02:05.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.66,0:02:11.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.45,0:02:15.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.05,0:02:20.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那是什么声音  难道是小偷？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.02,0:02:33.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛的说…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.60,0:02:39.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠星石？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.04,0:02:46.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.24,0:02:51.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红  我好想你的说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.91,0:02:53.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雏也是  小雏也是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.69,0:02:55.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.81,0:02:58.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红  真红
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.61,0:03:01.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红  真红
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.45,0:03:03.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了一个新的人偶吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.45,0:03:07.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.16,0:03:12.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}「翠星石」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.60,0:03:16.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  吃吧吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.69,0:03:20.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠星石也不用客气哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.90,0:03:22.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  茶泡饭海苔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.90,0:03:22.08,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}（「海苔」音同「纪」）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.42,0:03:22.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.22,0:03:25.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的适应能力未免太好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.61,0:03:29.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家里明明又多了个麻烦鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.49,0:03:34.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干…干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.75,0:03:38.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  翠星石被谁转动发条了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.78,0:03:42.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是  那孩子怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.51,0:03:48.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「那孩子」是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.29,0:03:49.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有其她的伙伴吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.44,0:03:52.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真让人期待啊  纯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.38,0:03:53.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.79,0:03:55.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.38,0:04:02.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最讨厌人类了的说～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.92,0:04:08.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠星石
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.19,0:04:13.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.86,0:04:15.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,食物是不可以拿来玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.24,0:04:27.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不喜欢吃鸡蛋糕吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.90,0:04:30.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我做草莓牛奶好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.06,0:04:32.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草莓  哇～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.61,0:04:38.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将所有的人类都说成是坏人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.69,0:04:41.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不像是身为园艺师的你会说出的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.54,0:04:45.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出了什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.83,0:04:52.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.45,0:04:57.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？  现在已经是睡觉的时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.11,0:05:00.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要睡的话  先把这个修好再睡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.41,0:05:07.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心  我们没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.41,0:05:09.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮箱里面是不通风的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.86,0:05:11.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也为我想想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.05,0:05:12.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.89,0:05:14.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.89,0:05:16.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.40,0:05:21.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是我行我素啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.85,0:05:27.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.81,0:05:31.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小不点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.42,0:05:32.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.46,0:05:37.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定…她是个很难缠的家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.06,0:05:52.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.62,0:05:58.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.74,0:06:07.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能超过那条线到这里来的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.57,0:06:08.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.58,0:06:10.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.50,0:06:14.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要待在自己的睡窝里  不能乱跑出来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.28,0:06:15.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了的说吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.52,0:06:17.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.64,0:06:20.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  居然到处乱跑的说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.92,0:06:21.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个家伙  给我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.08,0:06:24.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不要过来的说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.39,0:06:29.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在吵什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.21,0:06:31.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我  真红
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.39,0:06:35.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯  不要太吓她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.67,0:06:39.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子是姐妹之中胆子特别小  而且很怕生的一个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.17,0:06:41.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到…到底是谁吓谁啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.52,0:06:45.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好恶心  居然乱喷口水的说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.39,0:06:48.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.03,0:06:51.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雏也要玩追人游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.99,0:06:55.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我  放开我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.72,0:06:57.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  跑到哪里去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.59,0:07:01.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是缠人的家伙的说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.17,0:07:09.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个庭院是你整理的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.67,0:07:14.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  自己乱整理的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.96,0:07:16.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肥料放太多了的说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.41,0:07:19.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼爱它们是很好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.86,0:07:22.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  它们都在说「吃得太饱了」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.60,0:07:26.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠星石可以跟花朵说话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.69,0:07:27.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.85,0:07:29.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.12,0:07:31.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静一点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.49,0:07:35.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她对你来说可能会成为意想不到的收获
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.39,0:07:38.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,园艺师  翠星石的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.83,0:07:40.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.97,0:07:43.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不想知道她的力量！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.00,0:07:47.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就拜托你了  翠星石
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.51,0:07:52.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为人类做这种事  真是觉得很不值得的说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.22,0:08:01.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要开始做什么了吗？  姐姐我好兴奋哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.02,0:08:06.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水之梦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.54,0:08:25.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开门的说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.22,0:08:31.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你终于醒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.12,0:08:34.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个麻烦的小家伙的说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.22,0:08:37.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.26,0:08:49.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个没救的阴郁世界的说呢  看了就让人胸口郁闷的说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.30,0:08:51.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你带我来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.37,0:08:54.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个世界你应该很熟悉才对的说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.57,0:08:57.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是你的梦境
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.88,0:09:01.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你内心所映照出的世界的说了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.48,0:09:05.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是…我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.49,0:09:10.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯真的不要紧吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.39,0:09:11.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.96,0:09:13.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够找到通往梦境之门
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.23,0:09:16.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且能自由来去  这就是翠星石的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.90,0:09:17.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.54,0:09:26.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我进去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.85,0:09:27.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雏也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.08,0:09:29.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.24,0:09:31.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不怕吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.85,0:09:39.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果  可以稍微了解纯的内心世界的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.96,0:09:46.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪你在这里等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.86,0:09:48.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等着哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.39,0:09:49.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.80,0:09:56.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为纯一定不想让你看到他现在的内心景象
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.17,0:10:23.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是骗人的吧  这怎么可能是我的梦境
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.11,0:10:27.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叉叉七个  叉叉…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.05,0:10:29.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.92,0:10:35.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.35,0:10:38.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟这家伙单独相处  我真不知道该怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.48,0:10:41.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我要说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.36,0:10:42.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  那个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.57,0:10:43.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  你看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.92,0:10:48.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是参考书
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.81,0:10:51.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有好多参考书哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.48,0:11:08.64,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}(樱田纯)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.62,0:11:10.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是小不点的名字…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.23,0:11:24.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  快回座位坐好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.76,0:11:26.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.07,0:11:32.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樱田今天又缺席吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.03,0:11:34.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.60,0:11:36.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…到底出了什么事呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.99,0:11:48.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  花朵会讲话哦  好好玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.00,0:11:56.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  把这朵花摘下来送给纪  不知道她会不会高兴呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.13,0:11:58.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这家伙想干什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.97,0:12:00.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  笨蛋  不要过来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.57,0:12:03.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有道理  把它摘回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.26,0:12:54.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雏莓  飞到你那里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.93,0:12:56.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.60,0:13:04.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.10,0:13:07.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会露出这么滑稽的模样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.89,0:13:10.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追小汽车有什么好玩的说呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.41,0:13:17.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能让他展露笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.50,0:13:32.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.47,0:13:38.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.41,0:13:44.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  连胆子都是迷你型的说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.78,0:13:47.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么会飞起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.11,0:13:50.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会飞的只有你的说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.71,0:13:51.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.22,0:13:56.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果用小不点的肚量看世界的话  你永远都会是小不点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.87,0:14:17.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.92,0:14:28.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.19,0:14:33.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是你的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.06,0:14:36.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你想飞的话就能飞的说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.13,0:14:39.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.14,0:14:47.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在磨蹭什么的说  你这个小不点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.41,0:14:52.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个坏心眼的人偶…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.95,0:14:56.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要一直叫我小不点！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.97,0:15:23.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.07,0:15:26.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以小不点来说  表现算是很不错了的说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.51,0:15:33.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是当然的吧  这些只不过是用纸做出来的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.45,0:15:37.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  那只是普通的纸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.14,0:15:54.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好漂亮哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.04,0:15:56.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这个世界来说  算是很漂亮的说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.04,0:16:03.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么漂亮的  这个世界哪里漂亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.15,0:16:05.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看那里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.36,0:16:22.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那里去  纯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.87,0:16:26.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点走过去的说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.90,0:16:29.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这时候不飞呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.99,0:16:32.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.92,0:16:41.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是一棵很小的树
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.56,0:16:43.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么长得那么畸形
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.18,0:16:46.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这棵小树就是你自己的说哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.77,0:16:50.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个人在梦里的某处  都拥有一棵树
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.06,0:16:53.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦的主人变成一棵树  伸展他的树枝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.00,0:16:57.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在过程中创造他的心灵的说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.85,0:16:59.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这棵树是我？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.67,0:17:02.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  这孩子的成长受到了阻碍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.11,0:17:06.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我有园艺师的剪刀  就能帮你排除掉障碍的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.29,0:17:08.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,园艺师的剪刀？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.72,0:17:16.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.82,0:17:19.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我能为你做的只有这些
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.69,0:17:27.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水之梦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.91,0:17:40.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我的喷壶装满
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.54,0:17:43.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用甜美的水装满它
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.39,0:17:52.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稳健地  不受拘束地
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.93,0:17:56.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让绿叶闪闪发亮的舒展
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.11,0:18:16.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行的说  旁边的杂草挡住了  无法再伸展下去了的说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.68,0:18:19.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  好像变得有朝气多了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.55,0:18:22.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起的说  小树
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.95,0:18:25.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  不用跟我道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.69,0:18:28.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不是在跟你说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.06,0:18:31.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也太臭美了的说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.20,0:18:33.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！  你这个坏心眼人偶！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.71,0:18:34.86,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.20,0:18:35.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不要紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.18,0:18:40.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有了阳光  也有人为他浇水了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.44,0:18:44.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下就看你自己的生命力了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.64,0:18:53.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…居然还跑来你这种坏心眼人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.56,0:18:54.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间差不多要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.62,0:19:02.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果发条在这里停了  就会永远困在梦的世界里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.39,0:19:06.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才好啊  醒来以后  你们就不见了是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.76,0:19:10.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么一来  你也无法走出梦的世界的说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.61,0:19:13.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在现实世界里  你会变成一具活僵尸的说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.50,0:19:16.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…  你…你怎么不早说！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.55,0:19:17.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又没问的说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.21,0:19:19.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.88,0:19:22.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不知道怎么回去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.01,0:19:24.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.38,0:19:29.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘了吗  这里是你的世界哟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.29,0:19:38.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托  你未免飞得太快了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.34,0:19:39.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会掉下去的～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.40,0:19:42.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你们很罗嗦啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.94,0:19:49.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么？紧紧抓好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.32,0:20:02.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.75,0:20:05.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯  你平安无事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.36,0:20:06.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要抱着我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.06,0:20:08.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是人家…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.36,0:20:11.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是让人吓出一身冷汗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.50,0:20:15.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们回来了  纪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.73,0:20:16.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.20,0:20:21.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.87,0:20:24.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了  大家平安无事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.92,0:20:26.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑  真是够了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.68,0:20:28.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠星石
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.12,0:20:33.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要不要也跟纯缔结一下契约？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.00,0:20:37.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍…稍等一下  你擅自在胡说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.52,0:20:39.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他毕竟是我的仆从
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.61,0:20:42.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然多少有点难以相处  但基本上不是个坏人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.96,0:20:44.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是跟你说了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.06,0:20:47.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正有两个或三个  都是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.23,0:20:49.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里一样了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.67,0:20:55.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…不…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.48,0:21:00.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你的话  我死也不要的说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.14,0:21:01.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.97,0:21:03.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才乐得轻松呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.92,0:21:07.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  居然吼这么大声的说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.69,0:21:09.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个坏心眼人偶  给我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.12,0:21:12.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小不点居然追过来了的说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.43,0:21:14.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了不要叫我小不点！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.83,0:21:16.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪  好好吃～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.63,0:21:17.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.98,0:23:43.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经无法忍受了的说
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.31,0:23:43.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.34,0:23:45.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有什么怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.86,0:23:49.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小不点和小不点莓欺负我的说
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.35,0:23:50.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这还真是不平静啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.09,0:23:53.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我背黑锅嫁祸给我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.30,0:23:54.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还把我的皮箱弄得脏兮兮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.26,0:23:58.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是…看我这个新来的不顺眼的说
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.82,0:24:01.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然这样  我要展开全面对抗的说
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.99,0:24:03.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  蔷薇少女
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.07,0:24:06.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对这只蔷薇戒指发誓吧
